# Root build context (used by the carein-caddy multi-stage image, which builds
# the SPA from new-dashboard). Keep the ACR upload lean and secret-free.
**/node_modules
**/dist
.git
.github
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/.local
**/coverage
**/*.log
backend/data
backend/recordings
new-dashboard/coverage
# The caddy image only needs new-dashboard/ + deploy/container/Caddyfile; the
# backend image is built separately from the backend/ context (backend/.dockerignore).
